{
  "stem": "15197.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in a small town in Grojec with Ben.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the action, the Russian offensive, started in January, and we saw the Russians coming, we decided to go back to Warsaw, knowing that Warsaw is destroyed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nevertheless, we thought that certain people are alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew the bunker where a few of our Warsaw ghetto fighters were hiding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went to Warsaw by foot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were walking from Grojec to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We came-- of course, it was destruction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was army, and civilian, and certain houses were destroyed and bombed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a very sad and very bad situation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we went, and we met a few of people who were hiding.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We kept together in Warsaw, when the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And little by little, we get to know more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was sure that we are the only ones-- the only two, or three, or four.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But people started to come in from hiding places from the surrounding to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as the front went more and more to the West, more people, Jews, came into this city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But Warsaw was destroyed, and it was very difficult to find a place where to live.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So when Lodz, the city which was not destroyed, was liberated, many people went to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And Ben and I also decided to go to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In Lodz, a Jewish community started out, and a Jewish committee was organized.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the first people who saw me there turn to me to be the so-called director or manager of the Jewish Cultural Department.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I became the director of the Jewish Cultural Department.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And how the Jewish committee looked at that time was a peculiar, really, picture.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I was not lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This situation, none of my family survived, absolutely nobody.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
